<item>
            <title>[LU-12802] racer test stucks after test finishes</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12802</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;After racer test survives for a given time, it starts to cleanup.&lt;br/&gt;
And the parent racer.sh script waits the child racer/racer.sh&lt;br/&gt;
to exit. However sometimes, somehow, this sticks for a long time.&lt;br/&gt;
Sending a signal to remaining dd(or other) processes will wake up&lt;br/&gt;
the wait in parent racer.sh script immediately.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
